{{Water salinity}} This is a '''list of bodies of water by salinity''' that is limited to natural bodies of water that have a stable salinity above 0.05%, at or below which water is considered fresh.
Water salinity often varies by location and season, particularly with [[hypersaline lake]]s in arid areas, so the salinity figures in the table below should be interpreted as an approximate indicator.
